  "text": "A cocktail of three L. monocytogenes serotype 4b strains, J1-110 (food epidemic), N1-225 (human epidemic), MMS97-1 (raw beef ), were used. Growth conditions and cocktail preparation were according to Pang et al. [CITATION_1] .",
